CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772465147
OL,3,CMLA pay, Stormont reform, and
OL,4,Cgovernment by social media
OL,6,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,7,FPengelly added: "We will take time to
OL,8,Fgo through the recommendations in
OL,9,Fdetail."
OL,11,FUUP Leader Jon Burrows said his party
OL,12,F"respects the view of the independent
OL,13,Fbody" that recommended the uplift.
OL,15,FAlliance MLA Michelle Guy said her
OL,16,Fparty is focused on delivering for
OL,17,Fconstituents as a priority, not on pay
OL,18,Ffor elected representatives.
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@AOUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
