OL,3,CMLA pay, Stormont reform, and
OL,4,Cgovernment by social media
OL,6,FStormont's Official Opposition Leader,
OL,7,Fthe SDLP's Matthew O'Toole, said he
OL,8,Fcould understand why some would "raise
OL,9,Fan eyebrow" at the proposals in light
OL,10,Fof "what doesn't happen at Stormont".
OL,12,FThe Board also recommended
OL,13,F"significant financial sanctions" if
OL,14,Fan Executive is not formed following
OL,15,Fan election, or if at any time the
OL,16,Foffices of First Minister and deputy
OL,17,FFirst Minister become vacant following
OL,18,Frecent political turbulence.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
