OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772465147
OL,3,CMLA pay, Stormont reform, and
OL,4,Cgovernment by social media
OL,6,FThese include a reduction of 10% to
OL,7,FMLA salaries after six weeks ` and
OL,8,Fagain at weeks 12 and 18 ` if a
OL,9,Fgovernment is not formed in line with
OL,10,Fthe Northern Ireland Act 1998, which
OL,11,Fallows six months for its formation.
OL,13,FBoard chairman Alan Lowry said they
OL,14,Faim to ensure public money is spent
OL,15,Fwith accountability.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, a former First Minister has
OL,18,Fwarned a Stormont committee that there
OL,19,Fis "growing suspicion" within
OL,20,Fgrassroots unionism around reform of
OL,21,Fthe Stormont Assembly.
OL,26,@{D@DOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
