PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772465147
OL,3,CMLA pay, Stormont reform, and
OL,4,Cgovernment by social media
OL,6,FBaroness Arlene Foster sounded the
OL,7,Fwarning while giving evidence to the
OL,8,FAssembly and Executive Review
OL,9,FCommittee as part of its ongoing
OL,10,Freview into institutional reform.
OL,12,FThere have been calls from some
OL,13,Fquarters for reform of the Assembly
OL,14,Ffollowing recent collapses.
OL,16,FBaroness Foster told MLAs there must
OL,17,Fbe clear cross-community support for
OL,18,Fany reform.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
