PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772465147
OL,3,CMLA pay, Stormont reform, and
OL,4,Cgovernment by social media
OL,6,FFormer deputy First Minister Mark
OL,7,FDurkan also gave evidence to the
OL,8,Fcommittee on Tuesday morning.
OL,10,FMr Durkan, who had been involved in
OL,11,Fthe Belfast/Good Friday Agreement
OL,12,Fnegotiations, said he hoped some of
OL,13,Fthe mechanisms would be
OL,14,F"biodegradable", and might fall away
OL,15,Fas the environment changed.
OL,17,FHe said he wants to see reform,
OL,18,Fdescribing the current structures as
OL,19,Fhaving seen everyone's mandate
OL,20,Ffrustrated with various collapses of
OL,21,Fthe institutions over the years.
